snippet.title: Valentino Rossi The Game - MotoGP™ 2016
snippet.description: All the bikes, every rider, each class of the 2016 Season and the best game experience of all time for the official MotoGP™ game. Valentino Rossi The Game, in store across Europe on PC, PS4, Xbox One in a week! Save the date, June 16.
